Package: movepub
Title: Prepare biologging data for publication
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Peter", "Desmet", , "peter.desmet@inbo.be", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8442-8025"))
Description: Prepare biologging data for publication in a research repository or
    the Global Biodiversity Information Facility (GBIF, <https://gbif.org>).
    It includes functionality to convert Movebank (<https://movebank.org>) and 
    camera trap data to Darwin Core (<https//dwc.tdwg.org>).
